divs: Sighting Detailsmy cat woke me up about 5am this morning and as i looked down to see my cat, i glanced out the window and saw a far-off multicolored star-like object darting around in the sky. i woke my wife up from a sound sleep, told her i think i see a UFO and she witnessed it too. this object was darting around at incredible speeds and making complete start and stops instantly. also, it was pulsating in a beautiful multi-colored fashion. i was pretty blown away by the object since i've NEVER seen anything move like it did. it was by far the most beautiful and mysterious event i've ever seen in the sky. after about 6-8 minutes the object faded from sight by either moving too far away or simply faded out. as far as i can tell it was 40 miles or so away to the northeast somewhere above eastern Santa Rosa, CA or northern Sonoma area.
